title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Throwing Fits Q4 Shareholders AMA Pt. I
description:
The Core Four are back on the hot seat, answering your questions in the first half of our latest AMA. Topics include, but are not limited to: denim, fisticuffs, Barstool bridges burned, fashion shows, merch, lightweight outerwear, Chuck’s missing half, watches, rap, whip appeal, intellectual property, media diets, materialism, a week in the life and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
